ing: 1 (6 ounce) can small pitted black olives, drained
1 (6 ounce) package tomato basil feta cheese, crumbled
des: "This salad is easy, attractive, and a wonderful combination of flavors. For best results make a day ahead and let chill overnight."
ins: In a large bowl, combine the cauliflower, broccoli, cherry tomatoes, olives and cheese. Add enough dressing to coat, toss and refrigerate overnight.
